    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "LOCKHEED 100\nN8268R\nDELTA\nAIR FREIGHTER",
      "Delta's \"Hercules\" Air Freighter has a capacity of 45,000 lbs.\nThe huge craft has a clear pressurized compartment 8.5 ft. DELTA AIR LINES. INC. AIR FREIGHT\nhigh, 10 ft. wide, and 40 ft. long. Roller tracks in the floor\nP. O. BOX 3487\nallow speedy loading of standard container freight, inter-\nchanging with truck, rail, or marine transport. Door dimen-\nS. F. INT'L AIRPORT\nFRANCI\nISCO,\nCALIF.\n94128\nin the United States.\nARRIVAL NOTICE\nAir Freight\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nOn\nment of air freight from\nAirbill\nPcs /Wt.\nYour shipment may be picked up at:\nOffice hours\nStorage charges begin at 8:00 AM on:\nRate:\nThank you for using Delta Air Freight.\nIf you wish additional information,\nplease call:\nDELTA -ONE OF AMERICA'S PIONEER SCHEDULED AIRLINES\nPOST CARD\n2015.166.2521"
    ],
